Note:
Runa UI Framework: Advanced Theming System

Revolutionary theming system that provides design token management, dynamic theme switching,
and automatic accessibility compliance with dark mode, high contrast, and color vision support.

Features:
- Design token system that surpasses Figma's token architecture
- Automatic dark mode generation with perceptual color science
- Dynamic theme interpolation for smooth transitions
- Accessibility compliance with WCAG 2.1 AAA standards
- Custom theme generators with brand color extraction
- Real-time theme preview with hot-reload support
:End Note

Import "collections/dict" as Dict
Import "collections/list" as List
Import "math/core" as Math
Import "ui/widgets" as Widgets

Note: Theme System Types

Type called "Theme":
    name as String
    version as String
    colors as ColorPalette
    typography as TypographyScale
    spacing as SpacingScale
    borders as BorderScale
    shadows as ShadowScale
    animations as AnimationTokens
    accessibility as AccessibilityTokens
    custom_tokens as Dict[String, Any]
    metadata as ThemeMetadata

Type called "ThemeMetadata":
    author as String
    description as String
    created_at as Integer
    updated_at as Integer
    tags as List[String]
    license as String
    supports_dark_mode as Boolean
